<codeline><highlight class="normal">This<sp/>is<sp/>*internal*<sp/>documentation,<sp/>aimed<sp/>at<sp/>developers<sp/>that<sp/>contribute<sp/>to<sp/>the<sp/>QtPokit<sp/>project<sp/>itself.</highlight></codeline>
