<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Building<sp/>from<sp/>Source</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Prototypical<sp/>[CMake][]-based<sp/>out-of-source<sp/>build<sp/>and<sp/>test<sp/>process:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">~~~{.sh}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">cmake<sp/>-E<sp/>make_directory<sp/>&lt;tmp-build-dir&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">cmake<sp/>-D<sp/>CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release<sp/>-S<sp/>&lt;path-to-cloned-repo&gt;<sp/>-B<sp/>&lt;tmp-build-dir&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">cmake<sp/>--build<sp/>&lt;tmp-build-dir&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ctest<sp/>--test-dir<sp/>&lt;tmp-build-dir&gt;<sp/>--verbose</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">~~~</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>Test<sp/>Coverage</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Similar<sp/>to<sp/>above,<sp/>but<sp/>specify<sp/>`ENABLE_COVERAGE=YES`,<sp/>which<sp/>will<sp/>add<sp/>dependencies<sp/>on<sp/>[gcov][]<sp/>and<sp/>[LCOV][].</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">~~~{.sh}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">cmake<sp/>-E<sp/>make_directory<sp/>&lt;tmp-build-dir&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">cmake<sp/>-D<sp/>CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release<sp/>-S<sp/>&lt;path-to-cloned-repo&gt;<sp/>-B<sp/>&lt;tmp-build-dir&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">cmake<sp/>--build<sp/>&lt;tmp-build-dir&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ctest<sp/>--test-dir<sp/>&lt;tmp-build-dir&gt;<sp/>--verbose</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">cmake<sp/>--build<sp/>&lt;tmp-build-dir&gt;<sp/>--target<sp/>coverage<sp/>coverage-html</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>ls<sp/>&lt;tmp-build-dir&gt;/test/coverage.info<sp/>#<sp/>Coverage<sp/>tracefile.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>ls<sp/>&lt;tmp-build-dir&gt;/test/coverage/<sp/>#<sp/>HTML<sp/>report.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">~~~</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>Documentation</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Configure<sp/>the<sp/>same<sp/>as<sp/>above,<sp/>but<sp/>build<sp/>the<sp/>`doc`<sp/>and<sp/>(optionally)<sp/>`doc-internal`<sp/>targets.</highlight></codeline>
